<div id="review_3570963573" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3570963573" />
    <a title="Dawn C" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14948447-dawn-c"><img alt="Dawn C" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1535435406p2/14948447.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3570963573?book_show_action=true">Oct 02, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dawn C" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dawn C" href="/user/show/14948447-dawn-c">Dawn C</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/11720879-the-king-beyond-the-gate">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=media-audible">media-audible</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=loved">loved</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3570963573" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14729452367285783025">Another beautifully crafted SFF novel, character focused and full of philosophy and conversation, fun banter, deep friendships, humble heroes and brave cowards, a couple of strong women, and a very relatable and human cast. Gemmell managed to make me fall in love with everyone within a very short time, which is an admirable feat.<br/><br/>The novel, like the previous, has an afterword by the author who comes across as modest and kind, and I think this really shines through im his work and the characters h</span>
  <span id="freeText14729452367285783025" style="display:none">Another beautifully crafted SFF novel, character focused and full of philosophy and conversation, fun banter, deep friendships, humble heroes and brave cowards, a couple of strong women, and a very relatable and human cast. Gemmell managed to make me fall in love with everyone within a very short time, which is an admirable feat.<br /><br />The novel, like the previous, has an afterword by the author who comes across as modest and kind, and I think this really shines through im his work and the characters he creates.<br /><br />Definitely continuing with this saga.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14729452367285783025" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

