<span id="freeTextContainer8718841124386073828">Two generations after Druss the Legend, an evil ruler Ceska has risen to power. Three former protectors of the realm (Tenaka Khan, Decado and Ananais) are reunited in their determination to bring him down, gathering allies as they face overwhelming odds and dark forces. Strong women: leaders and lovers. Courage, bravery, righteousness, and sacrifice, the hallmarks of epic fantasy, abound here. Gory.<br/><br/>My favorite quote: <i>Love was what mattered. Love of one for one. The touching of hands, the touchin</i></span>
  <span id="freeText8718841124386073828" style="display:none">Two generations after Druss the Legend, an evil ruler Ceska has risen to power. Three former protectors of the realm (Tenaka Khan, Decado and Ananais) are reunited in their determination to bring him down, gathering allies as they face overwhelming odds and dark forces. Strong women: leaders and lovers. Courage, bravery, righteousness, and sacrifice, the hallmarks of epic fantasy, abound here. Gory.<br /><br />My favorite quote: <i>Love was what mattered. Love of one for one. The touching of hands, the touching of hearts. The warmth of belonging, the joy of sharing. There would always be tyrants. Man seemed incapable of existing without them. For without tyrants there would be no heroes, And man could not live without heroes.</i></span>
