<div id="review_3658543424" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3658543424" />
    <a title="fantasy fiction is everything" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything"><img alt="fantasy fiction is everything" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1555963206p2/57875854.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3658543424?book_show_action=true">Nov 25, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="fantasy fiction is everything" class="user" itemprop="url" name="fantasy fiction is everything" href="/user/show/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything">fantasy fiction is everything</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/16174983-the-king-beyond-the-gate">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=2020-fantasy-read-in-english">2020-fantasy-read-in-english</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=fantasy-fiction">fantasy-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=sword-and-sorcery">sword-and-sorcery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=military-fantasy">military-fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=uk-and-ireland-fantasy-author">uk-and-ireland-fantasy-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57875854-fantasy-fiction-is-everything?shelf=feel-good-fantasy">feel-good-fantasy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3658543424" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13515431352724455086"> Readers anticipated everything David Gemmell has written in Legend, the first book of Drenai Saga, all the material you&apos;re familiar with which can be found in The King Beyond The Gate. David Gemmell is good at creating a fascinating Heroic fantasy story. Heroes have dark histories, they fight with multitude of enemies, they redeemed themself in the end of story. they all have traumas after previous battle or other similar experiences. but They refused to accept that fact, they struggle for acco</span>
  <span id="freeText13515431352724455086" style="display:none"> Readers anticipated everything David Gemmell has written in Legend, the first book of Drenai Saga, all the material you're familiar with which can be found in The King Beyond The Gate. David Gemmell is good at creating a fascinating Heroic fantasy story. Heroes have dark histories, they fight with multitude of enemies, they redeemed themself in the end of story. they all have traumas after previous battle or other similar experiences. but They refused to accept that fact, they struggle for accomplishing their destiny or redeem themself. They may not succeed but they all show what the essential of a hero; how to overcome your weakness. I really love David Gemmell has accomplish a new level height of heroic fantasy, moreover influenced fantasy authors whom in new generation. <br /> Secondarily, inherited spirit of heroes is important subject in David Gemmell's books. If only heroes's individual stories which is not enough for completed heroic fantasy stories; most important is to inherited the spirit of hero to other people. Not just saved victims, moreover inspired them to be a hero!In the story, A hero who was supposed to save his kingdom because Ceska has send a army to pillage his kingdom but once he had to choose between continuing his journey or saving the children form the immediately crisis; he chose to save the children and died for it. His heroic act inspired one of the children to be a hero. For me David Gemmell is already a hero because he inspired a lot of fantasy writers. I wished I could meet him in privacy.<br /><br />I have a goal, stuck in Taiwan which is a filthy place do not to led down my head. I serve for, work for,contribute everything to fantasy fiction. yes I suffer a lot during this 2020 global crisis but my life should have something to strive for. I don't need to care I was not born in English country. Sometimes, I have difficulties work in Taiwan. I learn, grow to Contribute to fantasy world. work hard every day just to reach my goal and help something I really want to. No sorrows in hard efforts, because you didn't notice those trivial frustrations. A future's goal is await for me to accomplish.<br /> </span>
  <a data-text-id="13515431352724455086" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


